<paragraph pageId="15" pageNumber="234">Material examined</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="15" pageNumber="234">
(all from Russia, southwestern Siberia, Altai Province, Charysh District, ca. 4.5 km SE of Charyshskoye Village). 1 ♂ (ASU), 
